{"tid":596915,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"英文if only用法一問","createTime":"2018-03-18T06:33:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-29T15:54:21.000Z","uid":137768,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"77ebd03fae57aa897d8fcf6194ead4757172a442","tid":596915,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T06:33:44.000Z","msg":"Source:<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/tw.blog.voicetube.com/archives/24208/amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Ftw.blog.voicetube.com%2Farchives%2F24208%2Famp&d=Ji9LS5VDi9nEuzr0mj97mbr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=09be066b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/tw.blog.voicetube.com/archives/24208/amp</a><br />\n<br />\nif only<br />\n<br />\n但願<br />\n<br />\n1. If only 其實就是 If 的加強語氣，可以同時表達講者的願望與條件，例如要表達：「要是天氣放晴，我們就能出去玩了。」或「要是他能來，我就能當面謝謝他了。」時就可以用 If only。<br />\n<br />\ne.g.,&nbsp;If only&nbsp;I didn&rsquo;t have so much homework I could go to the party tonight.<br />\n唉，要是沒那麼多作業我就可以去今晚的派對了。<br />\n<br />\n2. 也可以單純表達願望，不表達條件。<br />\n<br />\ne.g.,&nbsp;If only&nbsp;I had a girlfriend.<br />\n但願我有個女朋友就好了。<br />\n<br />\n3.&nbsp; 有時候也可以寫成 If&hellip;only，也是表達願望。<br />\n<br />\ne.g.,&nbsp;If&nbsp;you would&nbsp;only&nbsp;trust me.<br />\n只要你能夠相信我。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第2同第3嘅用法其實formal 定informal? 喺香港考試作文可唔可以用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86c8d5fe88726c0f950e03940049560b757ae5cd","tid":596915,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T08:56:03.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c7dde46a822a8e19e864b000bd4b75e17230f3","tid":596915,"uid":100971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T15:54:21.000Z","msg":"可以<br />\n後面接虛擬語氣動詞"}]}